title: Top 10 TE Rankings + UDK-for-LIFE, Cup of Tea - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/17
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason countdown the top 10 tight ends for the 2021 season! Which difference-making TEs are worth targeting in drafts? Will rookie Kyle Pitts live up to the hype? Plus, don’t miss the latest edition of “Where There’s Smoke, There’s Fire!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 17th, 2021.
  
 Dominate your fantasy football draft with the 2021 Ultimate Draft Kit -- get the Draft Analyzer with the UDK+
  
 (08:05) - Where There’s Smoke, There’s Fire
 (08:40) - Phillip Lindsay, David Johnson
 (14:45) - Robert Tonyan Hype
 (21:30) - NFL News
 (26:55) - Top 10 Tight Ends
 (29:55) - Travis Kelce
 (33:25) - Darren Waller
 (39:25) - George Kittle
 (43:30) - Mark Andrews
 (48:00) - T.J. Hockenson & Kyle Pitts
 (54:55) - Tyler Higbee
 (57:00) - Robert Tonyan
 (58:15) - Mike Gesicki, Dallas Goedert
 (59:00) - Late Round Targets
